text:
Thank you for your help everyone. It works now with the background.
 unfortunately the cta is cut off when I run client tests on outlook 2016. Weird thing: its only cut off every second test. :face_with_raised_eyebrow:
here is the code. {% cta guid="{{ module.cta }}" %} is cut off in 50% of tests. see images. Any ideas?
Thank you for your help

```{# IL EMAIL HERO BOILERPLATE NOTES: padding only on td or tr elements. padding
on divs etc not supported #} {% macro render_logo(link) %}
&lt;div
  style="
    max-width: 158px;
    max-height: 158px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    padding: 0px;
    margin: 0 auto 0 0;
  "
&gt;
  {% set href = link.url.href %} {% if href %} {% if link.url.type is equalto
  "EMAIL_ADDRESS" %} {% set href = "mailto:" + href %} {% endif %}
  &lt;a
    href="{{ href }}"
    {%
    if
    link.open_in_new_tab
    %}target="_blank"
    {%
    endif
    %}
    {%
    if
    link.no_follow
    %}rel="nofollow"
    {%
    endif
    %}
  &gt;
    {{ caller() }}
  &lt;/a&gt;
  {% else %} {{ caller() }} {% endif %}
&lt;/div&gt;
{% endmacro %}
&lt;table&gt;
  &lt;tr&gt;
    &lt;td style="background-color: #add5f7"&gt;
      &lt;!--[if mso]&gt;
  &lt;v:rect fill="true" style="width:600; height: {{ module.module_height }};"&gt;
    &lt;v:fill
      aspect="atleast"
      type="frame"
      color="#add5f7"
      src="{{ module.background.src }}"
    /&gt;
    &lt;v:textbox&gt;
      &lt;![endif]--&gt;
      {% if module.show_module %}
      &lt;table style="width: 600px; border: none; border-collapse: collapse"&gt;
        &lt;tr style="border: none; margin: 0; padding: 0"&gt;
          &lt;td
            style="text-align: center; vertical-align: center; width: 100%; height: {{ module.module_height }}px; padding: 0; margin: 0; border: none; background-image: url({{ module.background.src }}); background-position: center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat;"
          &gt;
            &lt;table
              style="
                border: none;
                border-collapse: collapse;
                width: 100%;
                height: 100%;
              "
            &gt;
              {% if module.logo.src %}
              &lt;tr&gt;
                &lt;td
                  style="
                    width: 100%;
                    vertical-align: top;
                    padding: 40px;
                    margin: 0;
                  "
                &gt;
                  {% set sizeAttrs = 'width="{{ module.logo.width }}" height="{{
                  module.logo.height }}"' %} {% call render_logo(module.link) %}
                  &lt;img
                    src="{{ module.logo.src }}"
                    alt="{{ module.logo.alt }}"
                    {{
                    sizeAttrs
                    }}
                  /&gt;
                  {% endcall %}
                &lt;/td&gt;
              &lt;/tr&gt;
              {% endif %} {% if module.heading %}
              &lt;tr&gt;
                &lt;td
                  style="
                    width: 100%;
                    vertical-align: bottom;
                    padding: 0 52px 20px;
                    margin: 0;
                    text-align: left;
                  "
                &gt;
                  &lt;h2
                    style="
                color: {{ module.text_color.color }};
                font-size: 30px;
                line-height: 39px;
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
                text-transform: capitalize;
              "
                  &gt;
                    {{ module.heading }}
                  &lt;/h2&gt;
                &lt;/td&gt;
              &lt;/tr&gt;
              {% endif %} {% if module.description %}
              &lt;tr&gt;
                &lt;td
                  style="
                    width: 100%;
                    vertical-align: bottom;
                    padding: 0 52px 20px;
                    margin: 0;
                    text-align: left;
                  "
                &gt;
                  &lt;p
                    style="
                color: {{ module.text_color.color }};
                font-size: 15px;
                line-height: 20px;
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0 0 0 0;
              "
                  &gt;
                    {{ module.description }}
                  &lt;/p&gt;
                &lt;/td&gt;
              &lt;/tr&gt;
              {% endif %} {% if module.cta %}
              &lt;tr&gt;
                &lt;td
                  style="
                    height: 100px;
                    width: 100%;
                    vertical-align: middle;
                    padding: 15px 52px 0px;
                    margin: 2px 0 0 0;
                    text-align: left;
                  "
                &gt;
                  {% cta guid="{{ module.cta }}" %}
                &lt;/td&gt;
              &lt;/tr&gt;
              {% endif %}
            &lt;/table&gt;
          &lt;/td&gt;
        &lt;/tr&gt;
      &lt;/table&gt;
      {% endif %}
      &lt;!--[if mso]&gt;
    &lt;/v:textbox&gt;
  &lt;/v:rect&gt;
&lt;![endif]--&gt;
    &lt;/td&gt;
  &lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;```
